"uid":51746,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:22:16.000Z","msg":"因為大陸本身對呢類嘅監管係採用<br />\nDo nothing嘅狀態<br />\n合乎現有法例就無問題<br />\n但容易洐生出好多洗黑錢逃稅等問題<br />\n<br />\n而香港就採用邊走邊調節嘅方法<br />\n呢類公司乎合法例嘅情況下自行研發產品<br />\n到production出黎嘅時候<br />\n再審核現有嘅規例合唔合適<br />\n<br />\n所以大陸會出現更多咁嘅平台<br />\n但同時佢地都高風險好多<br />\n好容易出現龐氏騙局等嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申鳩up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024828decf63239e7f8f9f818ad191d6fddcaf37","tid":697990,"uid":8439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:22:45.000Z","msg":"因為香港金融體系太穩定 個餅一早分好曬 唔容許有人無啦啦叉隻腳埋黎"},{"pid":"9e2e6c833177681a5182f30ea08f4b3112fda728","tid":697990,"uid":39122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"42f96da2a81099a8dafc548ec6be9575277ddc7c","tid":697990,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d24c95fe0cc079f40f1b9cb69aacf0c5ee5e323","tid":697990,"uid":39122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3327ceacf06e500e4d88e4993f409aaed66039dd","tid":697990,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"唔係奶唔奶共,我係想討論下點解香港D金融機構唔做類似既野同依D平台有咩僭在風險?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:14:14.000Z","msg":"啲官唔想執多次迷債嗰種屎，<br />\n呢個咪係官場嘅風險。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:19:35.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人真係買依D基金蝕錢/得唔到預期既回報?<br />\n如果同香港D基金面對相同程度風險既話,咁香港D基金輸哂喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:24:55.000Z","msg":"Google keywords：&quot;理財產品&quot; &quot;違約&quot;<br />\n本都冇埋就未聽識嘅人中過，但係違約遲咗回水同最後冇息派就見過。"},{"pid":"5fdb5223a5a3761fdcb5eb56c5754bdc2422206c","tid":697990,"uid":151623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:28:21.000Z","msg":"如果唔係真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就google 錢寶網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj